{"tid":841292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[亞視翻生] 破先例！朱慧珊亞視節目於奇妙電視同步播","createTime":"2018-09-29T12:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T16:29:43.000Z","uid":17646,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ee3c08e9467f608da50c67eed370bf4711d2070c","tid":841292,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T12:40:19.000Z","msg":"由梁思浩與朱慧珊主持的亞視新節目《香港追擊搜》，這個時事資訊節目會討論社會熱話，類似當年《今日睇真D》，並加入前無綫新聞小花周嘉儀和黃紫盈，而最大突破是《香》將被有線奇妙電視購入，並將與亞視於10月8日同步播出，這個節目兩台同播之安排，可說是破電視台先例。主持梁思浩回覆東網稱：「哦！唔清楚，要等公司及奇妙自己公布，但若然事實當然係好事，有更多觀可以睇到個節目。」"},{"pid":"a57025279158e1f9aadc08600c89e47d9f1615fb","tid":841292,"uid":132587,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T12:46:09.000Z","msg":"有線咪撚痴咁多亞視啦 好快一齊收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2c1140500c1fc3291dbbc2f80cb0545eb4aee0","tid":841292,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a57025279158e1f9aadc08600c89e47d9f1615fb","tid":841292,"uid":132587,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T12:46:09.000Z","msg":"有線咪撚痴咁多亞視啦 好快一齊收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T13:07:12.000Z","msg":"有線老闆咪又係亞視嘅人"},{"pid":"415027ea2c5f7d3d89721e4582a8af3dbacf021c","tid":841292,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T13:09:19.000Z","msg":"如果77播百萬富翁應該會多noise啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017dbdd64a2e81849788dfda27eb66f7e3aad9c0","tid":841292,"uid":26601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"415027ea2c5f7d3d89721e4582a8af3dbacf021c","tid":841292,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T13:09:19.000Z","msg":"如果77播百萬富翁應該會多noise啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T13:22:40.000Z","msg":"梗係多NOISE啦<br />\n今時今日一百萬都學人叫富翁"},{"pid":"43907b60adb6a249df10013ce1fd05984868215b","tid":841292,"uid":87780,"l